<div id="imageContent0deebd17c7ac48e98d595920c7389713">
</div>
<p>We understand that coming to hospital can be a difficult and emotional time for lots of people.</p>
<p>If you are facing a time of illness, uncertainty or change you can meet with a member of our friendly<a href="https://www.imperial.nhs.uk/patients-and-visitors/chaplaincy-and-faith-services">chaplaincy team</a>Â who can provide emotional, pastoral and spiritual support, as well as a listening ear when you need it most.</p>
